title: Francisco Ugarte (footballer, born 1986)
text:
Francisco Patricio Ugarte Janietz (born 15 December 1986), is a <a href="Germany">German</a>-<a href="Chile">Chile</a>an <a href="Association%20football">football</a> defender who currently plays for <a href="Segunda%20Divisi%C3%B3n%20Profesional%20de%20Chile">Chilean Segunda División</a> side <a href="San%20Antonio%20Unido">San Antonio Unido</a>.
Personal life.
Born in <a href="Germany">Germany</a> to a <a href="Chilean%20people">Chilean</a> father and a <a href="Germans">German</a> mother, he holds dual nationality: German–Chilean. In Spanish, his last name Janietz is known as Nieto.
